data.description: The City of Philadelphia has completed a real estate tax reassessment, effective January 1, 2023. If you have any questions or concerns about the impact of this reassessment on future real estate taxes, please contact the City of Philadelphia. Listing agent- Christine Virata and Exp Realty, LLC are not involved in the City of Philadelphia’s tax reassessment and do not have any control over the results. Excellent investment property located in the Health Sciences Campus of Temple University close to Temple Hospital and Temple Medical School. This is an amazing opportunity for the savvy investor seeking to generate cash flow and appreciation. This property is conveniently located on public transportation and multiple bus lines. This duplex property offers 2 - 2 bedroom, 1 bathroom units. Both units are currently rented. The tenant is responsible for electricity and the owner pays for water. Both units have washer/dryers. The kitchens have upper and lower wood cabinets and granite countertops with ceramic tile flooring. There is hardwood flooring throughout the unit. The bedrooms are quite spacious and each unit has plenty of windows resulting in positive natural light. The first floor accepts Section 8 Vouchers. Roof Warranty transferable to the new owner- 20 years. Lastly, the property boasts an unfinished basement and a spacious backyard perfect for summer barbecues presenting an opportunity for further expansion/renovation or customization and design of space. Property being sold As-Is. Listing agent is related to the Seller.
